{"tid":2205706,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅訪蒙 逾百群眾高叫「保衞母語」","createTime":"2020-09-17T04:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T05:27:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2b98bf3229d95a3d2c839575523be2fc52532b","tid":2205706,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200917/S7T756BLPJDUXED2ORJCAQGBL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200917%2FS7T756BLPJDUXED2ORJCAQGBL4%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bkv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=b3753895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200917%2FS7T756BLPJDUXED2ORJCAQGBL4%2F&h=ed1b1341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200917/S7T756BLPJDUXED2ORJCAQGBL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n王毅訪蒙 逾百群眾高叫「保衞母語」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GXIjH-LWRPY8uOxjLKlLTEV5cDI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z3OUW46O4JB4BNOUXR7AEP3C7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGXIjH-LWRPY8uOxjLKlLTEV5cDI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ3OUW46O4JB4BNOUXR7AEP3C7E.jpg&h=4b5bb4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蒙古國前日有示威者持「請尊重你們的憲法」的橫額向中國外長王毅抗議。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古強推中小學以漢語授課引發罷課，當局近日軟硬兼施呼籲學生返校。錫林浩特市有學生因未在規定時間內回校上課，被取消高中入學資格，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內蒙罷課生遭開除學籍<br />\n<br />\n錫林浩特市蒙古族中學周二（15日）發文件通告，指高中生陶娜拉金未在規定時間內返校，被視為自願放棄入讀權利，將取消其高中入學資格。不過錫林浩特市的微信公號稍後刪除消息。該市及西烏珠穆沁旗前、昨日分別發出公告，對在規定時間前送子女入學的家長，發放獎金。否則取消各類補助，並追究家長法律責任。學生按照自動退學處理，取消學籍。<br />\n<br />\n中國外長王毅正出訪蒙古烏蘭巴托，蒙古總統巴特圖勒嘎昨指，蒙方高度重。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在王毅周二出訪期間，逾百名示威群眾聚集在蒙古國政府宮（Government Palace）前示威，高叫口號「保衞我們的母語」「王毅走開」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"96c4edb5f0c5a1eacdbebca30df45aa166d61004","tid":2205706,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒙古國前日有示威者持「請尊重你們的憲法」的橫額向中國外長王毅抗議。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返去就改憲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8710ea693bb9d113f83b7e42dfddfb5c2cc5143","tid":2205706,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c4edb5f0c5a1eacdbebca30df45aa166d61004","tid":2205706,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒙古國前日有示威者持「請尊重你們的憲法」的橫額向中國外長王毅抗議。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返去就改憲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"全英語教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}